               stealing, on the <rs id="t18280410-183-cd984" type="crimeDate">28th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280410-183-off983 t18280410-183-cd984"></join>, 1 watch, value 4l.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18280410-183-victim1055" type="victimName">
                  John 
                  Cargill
               <interp inst="t18280410-183-victim1055" type="surname" value="Cargill"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18280410-183-victim1055" type="given" value="John"></interp>
